who to install modules.
open power shell (in windows option).
Then Type pip install (flask)is one module It will start downloading flask from the internet. 
flask is used for making websites.
If u installed the flask successfully then type in power shell import flask it will show without any error.
python built-in modules are already installed in python.
some modules we have to download like (flask) from power shell.
To exit the power shell use exit()
pip is a package manager it will bring modules either from the internet or in python itself.
In a simple way, it collects the modules and is provided to python.
In pip there are two types of modules 1) built-in modules (which is already come with python).
2) external modules(which we download from the internet) in form of a power shell.
